cs.CL, cs.SD, cs.LG, cs.SD, cs.AI 

Reasoning: 
- cs.CL (Computation and Language) is the most likely category as the paper deals with multilingual acoustic models for speech recognition. 
- cs.SD (Sound) is also likely as the paper focuses on phonemes and phones, which are related to sound. 
- cs.LG (Machine Learning) is relevant as the paper proposes a joint model for language-independent phone and language-dependent phoneme distributions. 
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is relevant as the paper proposes a method to improve language processing using multilingual models. 
- cs.IR (Information Retrieval) is less likely as the paper does not focus on information retrieval specifically.
